data.description: Like new home awaits you! As you step inside, the impeccable design of this home unfolds, featuring high-end finishes that elevate every room. The kitchen offers a beautiful large island, laminate countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Spacious office or flex space conveniently located on the first floor, or use this as a guest suite providing convenience and privacy! Upstairs you'll run into the versatile bonus room, that can easily function as a 5th bedroom, offering flexibility for your family's needs. Let's talk about how spacious the primary room is! You'll find a large room with huge sitting area, spacious walk-in closet, & luxury primary bath & shower. So much value added into this home that easily creates a low maintenance, move in ready home! Recently added storm doors, and outside fencing area. The HVAC has been serviced twice a year for the last 5 years, and Bulwark exterminating service has serviced the home 3 times a year! Home warranty provided! This is a must-see!
